<th>Content Tier</th>
<th>Refresh Frequency</th>
<th>What to Check</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Top 10 traffic posts</td>
<td>Every 3 months</td>
<td>Stats, links, competitors, AI citations</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Posts in positions 6-20</td>
<td>Every 6 months</td>
<td>Keywords, intent, content gaps</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Low-traffic posts</td>
<td>Annually</td>
<td>Consolidation, redirect, or prune</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Evergreen reference posts</td>
